OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain spread northeast Wednesday with
OL,8,Foutbreaks becoming heavy Wednesday
OL,9,Fnight. This rain turns showery
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
